parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn or lock up, leading to loss of control of the vehicle, which can result in accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes stiff or hard to turn
the vehicle is difficult to control
the power steering warning light illuminates on the dashboard
and the vehicle may stall or decelerate suddenly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door locks and dashboard can cause safety issues, such as the inability to exit the vehicle in an emergency, and may lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The door locks do not open or close
the dashboard is detaching from the top
the steering wheel is trembling while driving
and the paint is peeling on the hood.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the axles and spindle nuts can cause loss of control of the vehicle, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The axles and spindle nuts are decaying and crumbling
causing the vehicle to vibrate or shake while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause loss of power steering, stalling, and other safety issues, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences a loss of power steering
with warning lights illuminating on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the oil cooler can cause oil leaks, leading to engine damage and potentially causing a fire.
symptoms: Oil leaking from the oil cooler

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause loss of control, accidents, and engine damage.
symptoms: jerking or lunging of the vehicle

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering can cause loss of control, accidents, and difficulty steering.
The failure of the drive shaft can cause loss of control, accidents, and engine damage.
The failure of the AWD system can cause loss of control, accidents, and difficulty driving.
symptoms: Erratic or unpredictable behavior of the AWD system

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause loss of control, accidents, and injury.
symptoms: Erratic or unpredictable behavior of the brake system

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the traction control and ABS systems can cause loss of control, accidents, and injury.
